{"tid":212264,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 你地有冇照過腦電圖","createTime":"2017-04-22T10:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T10:19:49.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d246a0c13752be09724ba87a2ee3ee8047f8a6c8","tid":212264,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"上年3月被青山醫畜捉過去照<br />\n<br />\n佢話癲癇都有可能導致某些症狀<br />\n<br />\n照完之後好似話腦電波有問題<br />\n<br />\n即係接近癲癇發作<br />\n<br />\n未至於真正發作<br />\n<br />\n不過都被佢塞我食epilim <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗返起好細個唔知做乜成日頭痛 暈<br />\n<br />\n好細個睇完戲，唔知係咪就係果套十萬伏特比卡超，然後頭暈作嘔頭痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小學果陣唔知做乜，望住本功課，之後開始頭暈作嘔，望住部電視畫面閃下閃下，我更加唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n同埋小學有幾次試過上上下堂暈＋作嘔，落醫療室休息下<br />\n<br />\n唔知小五定六，放學落樓梯，我成個人冇晒力，無法自控衝左落去<br />\n<br />\n班主任初初以為我玩野，不過我真係嘔左Ｄ水出黎<br />\n<br />\n我唔係玩野，真係暈到成個人冇晒力，同埋好想嘔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f7e4035a7cd0229f9558b6733057233f8fbfa5","tid":212264,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"我mc錯左兩題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c3657fbf318a8dbb79f7d97cc705738bce1a55","tid":212264,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我mc錯左兩題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考乜野"},{"pid":"5a8b9dba65e23f4d9273673b4a4d1ac09f129a4b","tid":212264,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我mc錯左兩題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考乜野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},